{"word":"Babes","slug":"babes","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Babes</b> In the mouths of, is praise perfected<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=16'>Mat 21:16</a><br/> A symbol of the guileless<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=8&verse=2'>Psa 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=25'>Mat 11:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=21'>Luk 10:21</a><br/> A symbol of the children of the kingdom of heaven<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=18&verse=6'>Mat 18:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=15'>Mar 10:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=17'>Luk 18:17</a><br/> Figurative of weak Christians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=2&verse=20'>Rom 2:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=3&verse=1'>1Co 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=5&verse=13'>Heb 5:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=2&verse=2'>1Pe 2:2</a><br/><a href='S:Children'>Children</a>; <a href='S:Parents'>Parents</a>"}]}